### Upstart organizational defaults ###
# Carried forward from teamupstart/force-orchestrator boilerplate so the new
# repo's existing patterns (multi-language toolchain artifacts, IDE state,
# infra bootstrap) keep working. force-orchestrator-specific entries follow
# below.

